trans-unit.source: Defines methods for reading the parts of a <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Define os métodos para ler as partes de um <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref> readers for each document in a <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção de <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref> leitores para cada documento num <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref> readers, one for each document in a <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref> leitores, um para cada documento num <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reader for the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref> with the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Obtém um leitor para a <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref> com especificado [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref>, if one exists, that is associated with the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref>, se existir, que está associado a <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> part of an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] sequence, see chapter 2 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre o <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>fazem parte de um [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] sequência, consulte o capítulo 2 no [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] especificação, que pode obter no [XPS: especificação e transfere licença](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> that contains the default printing options for the sequence; or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, if no print ticket exists for the document.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> que contém as opções de impressão predefinido para a sequência de; ou <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>, não existir nenhum pedido de suporte de impressão para o documento.

trans-unit.source: Gets the thumbnail image, if one exists, that is associated with the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a imagem em miniatura, se existir, que está associado a <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Uri> that represents the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for the sequence.
